E\xi^{2}=\underset{k=0}{\overset{n}{\sum}}k^{2}C_{n}^{k}\cdot p^{k}\left(1-p\right)^{n-k}=\underset{k=2}{\overset{n}{\sum}}k\left(k-1\right)C_{n}^{k}\cdot p^{k}\left(1-p\right)^{n-k}+\underset{k=1}{\overset{n}{\sum}}k\cdot C_{n}^{k}\cdot p^{k}\left(1-p\right)^{n-k}=\\
=p^{2}n\left(n-1\right)\underset{k=2}{\overset{n}{\sum}}\frac{\left(n-2\right)!}{\left(k-2\right)!\left(n-k\right)!}p^{k-2}\left(1-p\right)^{n-k}+np\cdot\underset{k=1}{\overset{n}{\sum}}\frac{\left(n-1\right)!}{\left(k-1\right)!\left(n-k\right)!}p^{k-1}\left(1-p\right)^{n-k}=\\
=p^{2}\cdot n\left(n-1\right)+np=np\left(pn-p+1\right)
